name: WSFS Financial Corporation
description: WSFS Financial Corporation is a publicly traded bank holding company headquartered in Wilmington, Delaware. Established in 1832, WSFS has a long history of serving its community and is recognized as one of the oldest banks in the United States. The company operates through its wholly-owned subsidiary, WSFS Bank, which provides a comprehensive range of financial services, including consumer and commercial banking, mortgages, and wealth management solutions. WSFS Bank is committed to delivering exceptional customer service, focusing on building long-term relationships with its clients. The bank has a strong presence in the Delaware and Pennsylvania markets, with numerous branches and ATMs. Additionally, WSFS has been expanding its footprint through strategic acquisitions, enhancing its capabilities and service offerings. The company prides itself on its community involvement and philanthropic efforts, supporting local initiatives and organizations. WSFS Financial Corporation has received various accolades for its performance and workplace culture, reflecting its commitment to excellence and innovation in the banking sector.
